  "title": "Software Engineer",
  "employer": "MandM Direct Limited",
  "descriptionTxt": "It's an exhilarating time to come join us here at MandM as we look to level up our IT Squad!\n\nWe're calling on all forward thinking, dynamic #Devs to join the force!\n\nThis is a Remote, Hybrid position (_*2 days per month in the office*_), our tech teams like to get together Bi-monthly for a F2F connect!\n\n*‘The Chosen one’*\n\n*Coding Connoisseur :* proven experience designing cooler than cool code\n\n*Scrum Chum:* work well with others, elevating the team by collaborating and sharing your expertise and ensuring all code is reviewed and signed off before release\n\n*Programming Prowess*: a whizz when it comes to developing innovative web applications, APIs and more.\n\n*Agile Advocate:* proven experience working Agile-ly, taking technical responsibility across the entire SDLC\n\n*Dev Devotee: *loves a challenge and has a knack for solving problems, applying agreed tools to achieve well - engineered outcomes\n\n*Code of choice:*\n\nC# and .Net CORE, Angular, NoSQL Databases, CSS, HTML and JavaScript.\n\n*'The Stack'*\n\nDesign and Development\n* of applications and Services using C#\n* of RESTful APIs using ASP.NET Core Web API\n* of databases and storage solutions in Google Cloud, i.e Spanner and Redis\n* of front end applications using Angular\n\nAnd bonus points if you've played around in the Cloud !\n\nThe tech alone not getting you excited?!\n\nWe also offer:\n* Competitive Salary: We believe in rewarding your brilliance.\n* Bonus Scheme: Your hard work deserves it.\n* Company Pension: Because its just makes money sense.\n* Birthday Bliss: Take the day off and celebrate YOU!\n* Staff Discount: Splurge on yourself!\n* Healthcare and Wellness: a little TLC does wonders!\n\nIf you are looking for your next epic role within our *software powerhouse *than apply right now!\n\nJob Types: Full-time, Permanent\n\nBenefits:\n* Additional leave\n* Canteen\n* Casual dress\n* Company pension\n* Employee discount\n* Free parking\n* Health & wellbeing programme\n* Life insurance\n* On-site parking\n* Referral programme\n* Sick pay\n* Store discount\n* Work from home\nSchedule:\n* Monday to Friday\n* No weekends\nSupplemental pay types:\n* Bonus scheme\n\n\n\nAbility to Commute:\n*  Leominster (required)\n\n\nWork Location: Hybrid remote in  Leominster",
