  "descriptionTxt": "Apply today: https://tsi.hire.skillsnow.com/apply/913/12595\n\n*Graduate Full Stack Developer*\n\n*Job description*\n\nWe are looking for smart, ambitious and inquisitive people to join the Software Institute's Graduate Full Stack Developer training programme to start in January 2024*.*\n\nUpon joining you will participate in our *remote, fast-track and paid 6 week training programme*. During the training you will learn Java development during a fulltime 6 week bootcamp, including other technologies such as Microservices, Databases and more. This is also a fantastic opportunity to be working on a transformation project with a leading company in their field, who are investing heavily in a hypergrowth technology platform which you will be involved with.\n\nThe Software Institute will continue to support you as you start your first consulting placement onsite with The Software Institute’s end client in *Solihull.*\n\n*No matter your academic background, you could thrive in this role if you are someone who:*\n* Enjoys problem-solving and creating solutions\n* Takes initiative\n* Can learn new concepts quickly\n* Can work well in a team and independently\n* Has excellent attention to detail\n* Enjoys working in a process-driven way\n* Is willing to speak up and offer ideas for change\n* Is able to build rapport with a diverse range of people\n\n*Salary and benefits*\n* Paid training from Day 1 of the program\n* Starting salary of *£18,000 during training, and rising to £25,000* on your first client placement\n* 22 days’ holiday plus eight bank holidays with an extra day added for each year you work with us\n* Pension contributions\n* Support and personal development planning to help you maximise your career progression\n* Ongoing training to achieve new professional certifications\n\n*What we are looking for*\n\nAll backgrounds welcome. We’re looking for individuals with a strong passion and aptitude for technology.\n\nAccepted degree subjects – Any, as long as you have exposure to either *Python, C++, C# or Java*\n\nApply today: https://tsi.hire.skillsnow.com/apply/913/12595\n\nJob Types: Full-time, Permanent, Graduate\n\nSalary: Up to £25,000.00 per year\n\nSchedule:\n* Monday to Friday\n\n\n\nAbility to commute/relocate:\n* Solihull, West Midlands: reliably commute or plan to relocate before starting work (required)\n\nEducation:\n* Bachelor's (required)\n\nWork authorisation:\n* United Kingdom (required)\n\n\nWork Location: In person",
