  "title": "Software Developer",
  "employer": "Utilink Consulting Limited",
  "descriptionTxt": "Utilink is a leading energy broker based in the vibrant region of North East. Specializing in providing tailored energy solutions to businesses of all sizes, Utilink stands out for its commitment to innovation and customer satisfaction. With a focus on leveraging the latest technologies and industry best practices, Utilink prides itself on delivering cost-effective and sustainable energy plans that meet the unique needs of each client.\n\nIf you are a passionate Software Developer with expertise in PHP Laravel framework, MySQL, API integrations, and GIT version control, we invite you to join our dynamic team at Utilink. Apply now and be part of innovative projects that challenge your skills and creativity.\n\n*Responsibilities*:\n* Design, develop, and maintain web applications using PHP Laravel framework.\n* Create and optimize database schemas using MySQL.\n* Integrate external APIs to enhance application functionality.\n* Collaborate with the team to manage code using GIT version control.\n\n*Requirements*:\n* Proficient in PHP and Laravel framework.\n* Strong understanding of MySQL database management.\n* Experience working with APIs to fetch and send data.\n* Familiarity with version control systems like GIT.\n\n*Additional Skills (Preferred):*\n* Knowledge of front-end technologies (HTML, CSS, JavaScript).\n* Ability to troubleshoot and debug issues effectively.\n* Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail.\n\n*Benefits:*\n* Free on-site parking\n* 25 days holidays (+ bank holidays)\n* Paid birthday off\n* Flexible working hours\n* Salary sacrifice schemes in place\n\nJob Types: Full-time, Permanent\n\nSalary: £40,000.00-£45,000.00 per year\n\nBenefits:\n* Additional leave\n* Casual dress\n* Company pension\n* Employee discount\n* Free parking\n* On-site parking\n* Private medical insurance\n* Work from home\nSchedule:\n* Monday to Friday\n* No weekends\n\n\n\nEducation:\n* A-Level or equivalent (preferred)\n\nExperience:\n* PHP: 3 years (required)\n\nAbility to Commute:\n* Sunderland, Tyne and Wear (required)\n\nAbility to Relocate:\n* Sunderland, Tyne and Wear: Relocate before starting work (required)\n\n\nWork Location: In person\n\n\nReference ID: Software Developer",
